## 🧠 **What’s New in v2025.1**

### 🔼 **Updated Base Score Formula**
```plaintext
Base_Score = 1.10 × (
    0.65 × Pitcher_Status_Score +
    0.15 × Previous_Season_RRI +
    0.25 × Pitcher_Ranker_Tier_Score
)
```

